lead_paragraph: Having promised to favor you (or it may be to trouble you) with another letter, acquainting you with our whereabouts, particulars, , in regard to the late foray upon one of the possessions of her Spanish Majesty, I will proceed to particularise as laconically as possible the facts as they occurred from the moment we landed until our delivery into the hands of the Cuban authorities.

headline.main: The Cuban Expedition--Letter from Another Prisoner.; From The N.O. True Delta, Sept. 23.
